nodes.text: A Human male was on the planet Manaan and was aware of both Sunry and Elassa Huros's true identities—he was an agent of the Galactic Republic's intelligence community and she was a Dark Jedi. While the Jedi Revan was investigating Huros's murder by Sunry, the man approached the Jedi and told him to search the Republic and the Sith embassies in Ahto City for more information.
